videos.description: Quentin Goodin finds Trevon Bluiett coming off the screen and he knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Xavier's Bluiett is money from downtown

videos.description: Kyron Cartwright gets the steal then weaves his way through defenders for a nice bucket.
videos.headline: Cartwright shows speed on Providence bucket

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett finds Tyrique Jones with a nice pass cutting to the basket and he throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Bluiett's smooth dish leads to bucket

videos.description: Makai Ashton-Langford drives and makes a nice up-and-under move to score the buzzer-beater.
videos.headline: Providence's Langford beats the buzzer

videos.description: Paul Scruggs drives and makes a nice feed to Sean O'Mara for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Scruggs-O'Mara connection leads to big play

videos.description: Maleik White gets the steal then throws down the hard two-handed slam.
videos.headline: White throws down the angry slam for Providence
